Class ChiselUIPage

java.lang.Object
com.Ev0sMods.Ev0sChisel.ui.ChiselUIPage
public final class ChiselUIPage extends Object
Chisel UI page – shows available substitution blocks as icon buttons organised into four tabs: Blocks, Stairs, Half Slabs, Roofing. Supports pagination when the number of items exceeds one page.

    • open

      public static void open(com.hypixel.hytale.server.core.universe.PlayerRef playerRef, com.hypixel.hytale.component.Store<com.hypixel.hytale.server.core.universe.world.storage.EntityStore> store, com.hypixel.hytale.math.vector.Vector3i blockPos, com.hypixel.hytale.server.core.universe.world.World world, String[] substitutions, String[] stairs, String[] halfSlabs, String[] roofing, ChiselUIPage.Tab activeTab, int page)
      Opens (or re-opens) the chisel UI for the given player, showing the items from the selected tab at the given page.
      Parameters:
      playerRef - the player who is using the chisel
      store - entity store (needed by PageBuilder)
      blockPos - the world position of the block being chiselled
      world - the world instance (used to write the new block)
      substitutions - full-block substitution keys (may be empty/null)
      stairs - stair block keys (may be empty/null)
      halfSlabs - half-slab block keys (may be empty/null)
      roofing - roofing block keys (may be empty/null)
      activeTab - the tab to display
      page - zero-based page index
